info.description: # librelingo\_json\_export.export #### export\_course ```python export_course(export_path: str, course: Course, settings=None) ``` Writes the course to JSON files in the specified path. ### Usage example: ```python from librelingo_yaml_loader import load_course from librelingo_json_export.export import export_course course = load_course("./courses/french-from-english") export_course("./apps/web/src/courses/french-from-english", course) ```
info.name: librelingo-json-export
info.summary: Export LibreLingo courses in the JSON format used by the web app
